channel.title: Two Questions
channel.description:
-What do I search in client.java for my DEATH respawn? When I die, I go to the old Home's death place, and have the same outfit the original starter was. I want to change the Death Respawn entirely to my new home, and make it keep the character's current look. (Look = Equipment AND ::char settings)
and
-How can I make an object teleport you somewhere when you click it? Searching didn't work, and I can't seem to make it work.

item.title: Two Questions
item.dc:creator: @Epic_Ancient Epic Ancient
item.description:
@Epic_Ancient wrote:

Couldn’t find deathstage = 2. I searched “death” and found nothing about coords. Are you sure it’s in client.java?

And Idk what you meant by the second one.

Read full topic

item.title: Two Questions
item.dc:creator: @_Joshua1 |Joshua|
item.description:
@_Joshua1 wrote:

Look up deathstage == 2 in Client.java and edit the coords it takes you to upon death.
Also, for the object clicking teleport make a case for the object… You can copy it by looking for a case for a tree for woodcutting IE. search Case 1276 and go from there. :rolleyes:
